{"id": "1426119922811146360", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：命运前奏之曲 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲**\n噩兆与乐音交织降临，他亦敌亦友，他扑朔迷离。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"Destiny's Prelude\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: Destiny's Prelude**\nIll omens and sweet melodies interwove upon his arrival. Inscrutable as he is, he may be your friend, or your foe.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:11:25.625000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 19}, {"emoji": "satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "H_immerse", "emoji_id": "1426122347643146250", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1426119923297681448", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1437355, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426119923297681448/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69ccd32d&is=69cb81ad&hm=17585a996638c4bd5d7b97d5fb747b2336a37e51b4c2ced77e17a83a734d42bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426120097600241694", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 恢弘律令-The Grand Melody-**\n\n噤声，前行。序曲早已奏响。\n我会伴你走向，注定的、无上的、至美的终章。\n\nSilence. Advance. The prelude has long since begun.\nI'll walk you to the destined, sublime, and ultimate finale.", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:12:07.298000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Jointhefun1", "emoji_id": "1400771646293282918", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "H_immerse", "emoji_id": "1426122347643146250", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1426120096899797082", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 967846, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120096899797082/1.jpg?ex=69ccd357&is=69cb81d7&hm=55ce91115c57b68be6333fda4f86fb334bd0c11dcb63deed1fd4de4ffad80462&"}, {"id": "1426120097239400469", "filename": "01._-The_Grand_Melody-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25202220, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120097239400469/01._-The_Grand_Melody-.wav?ex=69ccd357&is=69cb81d7&hm=8d688ab6ea83bd72005d17b78d964b85cad2db9ff8be45056cb56f8df121c159&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426120173240189001", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 薄暮-At Dusk-**\n\n人总是容易在黄昏时陷入恍惚与沉默，因为所剩无几的太阳，因为尚未被消耗殆尽的好时光。\n\nPeople often fall into a daze and silence at dusk—for the dwindling sun, for the meager good times.", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:12:25.332000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426120172586139658", "filename": "02._-At_Dusk-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20558106, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120172586139658/02._-At_Dusk-.wav?ex=69ccd369&is=69cb81e9&hm=e2fecb1d573ec905f8033de1eae102629724329cc9707b3c9002cbd693e53d6c&"}, {"id": "1426120173231935609", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 940865, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120173231935609/2.jpg?ex=69ccd369&is=69cb81e9&hm=d0a2a96517df8d2eb5df6b8e947ad8c954aeb11113613195f45af6824c3abd64&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426120300034265130", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 指挥家的谜语-The Conductor's Riddle-**\n\n你既不擅长音乐，也不喜欢解谜。\n但他平静且优雅地将你编织进交响，神秘而失礼地抛出了他的谜语。\n\nYou are neither skilled in music nor fond of solving puzzles.\nBut he weaves you into the symphony, calmly and elegantly, presenting his riddle with a mysterious insolence.", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:12:55.562000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426120299430019112", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 982890, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120299430019112/3.jpg?ex=69ccd387&is=69cb8207&hm=470fdb65317901000f3a79529869c351639eb051c2e6b55c71db0d819aecb770&"}, {"id": "1426120299698585631", "filename": "03._-The_Conductors_Riddle-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 14511008, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120299698585631/03._-The_Conductors_Riddle-.wav?ex=69ccd387&is=69cb8207&hm=80f3982a30817dcb9d704f85024a7a576755b6708144636ca6757e586fd79024&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426120393327902831", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 踏对节拍-Keep the Beat-**\n\n捕捉每一个音符，落在正确的节奏上。\n小心，注意，面对挑剔的指挥家，行差踏错会让你落入万劫不复的境地。\n\nSeize every single note and strike the proper tempo.\nTake heed, be wary. Any small mistake before the fastidious conductor will lead you to utter ruin.", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:13:17.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "satisfy", "emoji_id": "1400771690321154110", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "H_immerse", "emoji_id": "1426122347643146250", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "✨", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1426120392514211910", "filename": "04._-Keep_the_Beat-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33000752, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120392514211910/04._-Keep_the_Beat-.wav?ex=69ccd39d&is=69cb821d&hm=ff0839e904f1952988aae7727869e3184d868a2b463955cb1816cd81b712d041&"}, {"id": "1426120392900214868", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 965877, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120392900214868/4.jpg?ex=69ccd39d&is=69cb821d&hm=334990fd21d7230a74f8d2a1f2875378fc6547c3102bd2f5bbf9510510b47c7e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1426120552958918756", "channel_id": "1426119922811146360", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 命运将至-Fate Is Looming-**\n\n战胜我们，杀死我们。然后，拯救我们。\nDefeat us. End us. And then, save us.", "timestamp": "2025-10-10T08:13:55.864000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1426120551914672178", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 964769, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120551914672178/5.jpg?ex=69ccd3c3&is=69cb8243&hm=3ecb35dcd720e39620306c9ae4da79e2aaa9c21cc96f49bf94687d20ad4c1cb0&"}, {"id": "1426120552330035240", "filename": "05._-Fate_Is_Looming-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 28858046, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1426119922811146360/1426120552330035240/05._-Fate_Is_Looming-.wav?ex=69ccd3c3&is=69cb8243&hm=29859c88c4b9a0b8b2208e5053af977c2086eedf2ff11ac5226b084fcd83b3c9&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1426119922811146360", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：命运前奏之曲", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
